  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >One fateful day, without any warning, the labyrinthine city of Orario was transformed.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In the sunken Orario, Bell and his group follow the trail of the characters as dictated in the heroic tale.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >What they find there are an abundance of thoughts and feelings not depicted in \"Fullland of Water and Light\".</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A story tracing the hero's trials and truth now unfolds...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Control Bell Cranel or Ais Wallenstein in this side-scrolling RPG, defeating monsters and advancing through stages to complete the story!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253030/extras/ee5cc12e0b3fc7f531420ac97e01f8e6.avif?t=1741791629\" width=616 height=94 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253030/extras/08698a87599384ba6a51e17ad829ff99.avif?t=1741791629\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253030/extras_big/08698a87599384ba6a51e17ad829ff99.avif?t=1741791629 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A completely new story based on an original concept by the \"Danmachi\" series' author, Fujino Omori.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The main character, Bell Cranel, and his friends trace the hidden truths of the hero's tale in the submerged city of Orario.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253030/extras/73206b10271c2b17158be1f07d7b560e.avif?t=1741791629\" width=616 height=94 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253030/extras/bf9b23d7b987eb9894b04fa9069e05ed.poster.avif?t=1741791629\" width=632 height=356 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253030/extras/bf9b23d7b987eb9894b04fa9069e05ed.webm?t=1741791629\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253030/extras/bf9b23d7b987eb9894b04fa9069e05ed.mp4?t=1741791629\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Control Bell Cranel and Ais Wallenstein using both magic and sword fighting to defeat enemies and clear the stage.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You'll also be able to fill the \"Super Special Move Gauge\" to unleash \"Argo Vesta\" and \"Lil Rafaga\" to overcome difficult battles.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253030/extras/435eb9a063552835813a8e4706abf351.avif?t=1741791629\" width=616 height=94 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253030/extras/18ed2c4d1118b8c39e1933f5d7da588d.poster.avif?t=1741791629\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253030/extras/18ed2c4d1118b8c39e1933f5d7da588d.webm?t=1741791629\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253030/extras/18ed2c4d1118b8c39e1933f5d7da588d.mp4?t=1741791629\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Parry enemy attacks with perfect timing to launch an explosive counter attack.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your attack power will greatly increase when your counter attack is released.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Show off your skills with this high risk, high reward move.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253030/extras/018a4e0d8cd87f57d0fd761df543fbcd.avif?t=1741791629\" width=616 height=94 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253030/extras/dffbfb7ffb480d814c9e03b08fa45bd4.avif?t=1741791629\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253030/extras_big/dffbfb7ffb480d814c9e03b08fa45bd4.avif?t=1741791629 width=800 height=444 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >During battle, friends you have battled with will join you as allies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Show off the skills you've acquired over the course of your adventure as you face off against oncoming monsters.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >One fateful day, without any warning, the labyrinthine city of Orario was transformed.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In the sunken Orario, Bell and his group follow the trail of the characters as dictated in the heroic tale.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >What they find there are an abundance of thoughts and feelings not depicted in \"Fullland of Water and Light\".</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A story tracing the hero's trials and truth now unfolds...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Control Bell Cranel or Ais Wallenstein in this side-scrolling RPG, defeating monsters and advancing through stages to complete the story!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253030/extras/ee5cc12e0b3fc7f531420ac97e01f8e6.avif?t=1741791629\" width=616 height=94 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253030/extras/08698a87599384ba6a51e17ad829ff99.avif?t=1741791629\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253030/extras_big/08698a87599384ba6a51e17ad829ff99.avif?t=1741791629 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A completely new story based on an original concept by the \"Danmachi\" series' author, Fujino Omori.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The main character, Bell Cranel, and his friends trace the hidden truths of the hero's tale in the submerged city of Orario.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253030/extras/73206b10271c2b17158be1f07d7b560e.avif?t=1741791629\" width=616 height=94 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253030/extras/bf9b23d7b987eb9894b04fa9069e05ed.poster.avif?t=1741791629\" width=632 height=356 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253030/extras/bf9b23d7b987eb9894b04fa9069e05ed.webm?t=1741791629\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253030/extras/bf9b23d7b987eb9894b04fa9069e05ed.mp4?t=1741791629\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Control Bell Cranel and Ais Wallenstein using both magic and sword fighting to defeat enemies and clear the stage.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You'll also be able to fill the \"Super Special Move Gauge\" to unleash \"Argo Vesta\" and \"Lil Rafaga\" to overcome difficult battles.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253030/extras/435eb9a063552835813a8e4706abf351.avif?t=1741791629\" width=616 height=94 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253030/extras/18ed2c4d1118b8c39e1933f5d7da588d.poster.avif?t=1741791629\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253030/extras/18ed2c4d1118b8c39e1933f5d7da588d.webm?t=1741791629\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253030/extras/18ed2c4d1118b8c39e1933f5d7da588d.mp4?t=1741791629\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Parry enemy attacks with perfect timing to launch an explosive counter attack.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your attack power will greatly increase when your counter attack is released.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Show off your skills with this high risk, high reward move.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253030/extras/018a4e0d8cd87f57d0fd761df543fbcd.avif?t=1741791629\" width=616 height=94 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253030/extras/dffbfb7ffb480d814c9e03b08fa45bd4.avif?t=1741791629\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3253030/extras_big/dffbfb7ffb480d814c9e03b08fa45bd4.avif?t=1741791629 width=800 height=444 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >During battle, friends you have battled with will join you as allies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Show off the skills you've acquired over the course of your adventure as you face off against oncoming monsters.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
